summary: SummaryHighlightsClean IngredientsSustainable PackagingBenefit Cosmetics They're Real! Lengthening Mascara is a lengthening mascara that curls, volumizes, lifts and separates lashes for beyond belief beauty! The jet black, long-wearing formula won't smudge or dry out. A specially designed brush reveals lashes you never knew you had!
details: DetailsBenefitsLengthens, curls, volumizes, liftsLong-wearing formulaCustom domed-tip brushAvailable in full size and miniResearch Results94% saw dramatic length & volume*Â Â 94% saw visible lift*Â Â 100% saw long-wearing results*Â Â *Results observed in a consumer panel surveyÂ Item 2231443How To UsePosition wand horizontally & wiggle brush from side to side, base to tip, to achieve maximum volume, length & lift. Hold wand vertically & stroke upward to curl & separate. Layer generously as desired.BEAUTY TIP: Want a big, doe-eyed look? Fan corner lashes outward with the custom-domed tip. May Contain: CI 77499 (Iron Oxides), CI 77007 (Ultramarines). NÂ° 16510.Disclaimer: Product ingredient listings are updated periodically. reviews.headline: BEST MASCARA
reviews.comments: I have small lashes and have tried MANY different brands, expensive ones too, and ALWAYS go back to  this brand.   The mascara DOES make my lashes look longer, not clumpy, and stays on until I take it off.

reviews.headline: They're Real Mascara
reviews.comments: My go to mascara for years. Try other brands and always come back to using this one !

reviews.headline: Terrible!
reviews.comments: smudged under my eyes every time no matter what I did.

reviews.headline: Well, there ya go
reviews.comments: I love the look of this mascara on. It lengthens and seperates while adding sexy volume. However! It smudges desperately bad. So badly in fact that I cannot enjoy it. The effect it has on my lashes is so divine. But I look like a mess with black smudges on my face that take away from the attractiveness of my makeup overall. I'm so heart broken. The search continues...

reviews.headline: This is the best!
reviews.comments: This was the best mascara I've ever used. I am 58 years old and have been through many mascaras. This one is by far the best. Will buy extras to keep on hand so I'll never run out.

reviews.headline: I only buy this product for my lashes!
reviews.comments: They're Real Mascara and the primer are a MUST!  I am complimented so often on my lashes.  My hairdresser even asked me if I had professional lashes "on"!!!

reviews.headline: I like the product but the price continues to increase.
reviews.comments: This product is rarely on sale.

reviews.headline: Just Average
reviews.comments: Middle of the road product.  Tends to clump upon application.  Also, smudges badly if you touch your eyes at all throughout the day.  Sadly, this product is not for me.

reviews.headline: Disappointed.
reviews.comments: I have used this mascara for over 3 years.  I was obsessed with it!!!! I don't know what has happened over the past six months but the product has completely changed.  Dried out almost immediately multiple times! I have sadly moved on.

reviews.headline: the best mascara around
reviews.comments: I love this mascara. It is the best for long, full lashes for my eyelashes

reviews.headline: Great mascara
reviews.comments: In the market for a new mascara, so I bought this in the mini size and I love it. Adds length and volume!

reviews.headline: Cursed
reviews.comments: It all transferred to my undereye and THEN decided to become entirely waterproof. Now i look like a racoon, 0% on my lashes 100% under my eye. Raging because my makeup remover wont take it off!!!

reviews.headline: Love this!
reviews.comments: Great mascara, have bought several. Lengthens lashes and coats without being clumpy. Highly recommend!

reviews.headline: Longwearing mascara that goes on smooth
reviews.comments: This is an excellent longwearing mascara that goes on smooth with very little clumping. Though it's not waterproof, it definitely makes it through a long day without transferring or sliding. To compare climates - we live in a dry climate with very little humidity.
one of the best mascaras i've tried recently. definitely recommend it.

reviews.headline: Best mascara!!
reviews.comments: Best mascara, do it's best after using a etelash curler ðŸ˜‰ but its pricey!!!

reviews.headline: Dried out mascara
reviews.comments: I bought a 2 pk, use it daily. Went to use second mascara and it was dried out. Return window passed and return or exchange was refused.  Very disappointed. Thus was thru Benefits themselves

reviews.headline: My favorite
reviews.comments: My favorite

reviews.headline: BRING BACK BROWN
reviews.comments: this is the greatest mascara on planet earth. doesnt flake. builds beautifully. PERFECT spoolie, but i dont wear black mascara, its much too harsh on my skintone. pleaseeeee bring back brown ;( i miss it so much!!!!

reviews.headline: Flakiest mascara I've tried in awhile
reviews.comments: I have sensitive eyes, so at the end of the day most mascaras ive tried end up flaking into my eyes and irritating them. Ive found more mascaras are definitely more guilty of this then others. I was really excited to try this mascara but what was really disappointed to find that it took too long to dry after applying and would smear and I never made it to the end of the day without my eyes getting super irriated from the mascara. Gave up after about 4 uses and i went back and bought a mascara I know wont give me the same issues

faceoff_positive.comments: Wow, I don't have enough great things to say about this. I found out that my boyfriend who I was going to marry cheated on me, so I cried for nearly 7 hours one day with this mascara on. To my shock, this mascara was still in place and only smudged a little bit. And when I say I cried, I mean I was in fetal position on the ground...and this mascara still held up. So y'all, go buy this thing because I will forever swear by it and if I could marry it, I would. Cause we all know it would be more faithful than my man could ever be. Solid 10/10
faceoff_positive.headline: I would 1000000% buy this again

faceoff_negative.comments:
How disappointing - I finally drop some money on a mascara and it didn't even compare to the CoverGirl LashBlast I normally use. My friend did like the look, but I like it when my eyelashes look long AND full. If you try to layer it, it just clumps up.
I even put They're Real on one eye and the CoverGirl on the other eye and asked a GUY at work which was better and he said, without a doubt, the CoverGirl eye was just as long but much more volume. So don't waste your money.
faceoff_negative.headline: Not at all impressed
